icient diligence. In some instances, Voyager got lucky=E2=80=94for example,=
 Firms B, C, and D and certain others repaid Voyager.
With respect to Firm A, Voyager was similarly reckless but, unfortunately f=
or Voyager=E2=80=99s customers, far less lucky. Voyager transferred Firm A =
over $650 million worth of digital assets commodities=E2=80=94an amount suf=
