fused to allow. They=E2=80=99ve previously cited market manipulation, among=
 other reasons, for not granting an endorsement. However, the incident also=
 serves as a reminder that Bitcoin=E2=80=99s price can easily be moved by g=
ossip or hearsay.

Again, I am not=C2=A0that=C2=A0sympathetic to the SEC=E2=80=99s objections =
to a spot Bitcoin ETF. But this story makes me a little more sympathetic? T=
he price of Bitcoin jumped by 10% because people on social media were sayin=
g, falsely, that BlackRock=E2=80=99s spot Bitcoin ETF was approved. Seems l=
ike the sort of thing that could be manipulated!
