=E2=80=99re gonna deduct $11.95 from your paycheck, don=E2=80=99t do it aga=
in.=E2=80=9D And then the bank would save $11.95 per analyst.
Which is not worth it. But it would also get a=C2=A0few=C2=A0analysts who w=
rite back indignantly with elaborate fictional stories about the chain of e=
vents that led to them ordering two entrees with their meal allowances. And=
 then it could investigate those stories, and if they turn out to be false,=
