<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I guess some foundational=C2=A0questions in cr=
ypto are, if you got all the most dedicated crypto enthusiasts in the world=
 together in one place and let them build a new society together, would tha=
t new society run on the blockchain? Would it use cryptocurrency for paymen=
ts? Lol, no.=C2=A0Ethereum founder Vitalik Buterin threw a two-month-long E=
thereum conference at a resort in Montenegro, and=C2=A0<a href=3D"https://l=
ink.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/33044024.256428/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cucGFsbG=
FkaXVtbWFnLmNvbS8yMDIzLzEwLzA2L3doeS1pLWJ1aWx0LXp1emFsdS8_cmVmPXRoZWJyb3dzZ=
